            Our other point was that:
            <q>Both the Environment Agency and local authorities need more defined responsibilities and improved powers to combat the growth in fly-tipping.</q>
            
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_265wh' title='Col. 265WH &mdash; HC Deb 21 May 2003 vol 405 c265WH' name='column_265wh' href='#column_265wh' rel='bookmark'>265WH</a>
