            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_268wh' title='Col. 268WH &mdash; HC Deb 21 May 2003 vol 405 c268WH' name='column_268wh' href='#column_268wh' rel='bookmark'>268WH</a>
            that income from the fines should be used to help to pay for the costs of enforcement? The key issue is enforcement, which requires more expenditure and greater resources.
          </p>
